WebWikipedia2009

The undirected graph WebWikipedia2009 has 1864433 nodes and 4507315 edges.

RAM requirements

The RAM requirements for the nodes and edges data structures are 330.34MB and 23.46MB respectively.

Degree centrality

The minimum node degree is 1, the maximum node degree is 2624, the mode degree is 1, the mean degree is 4.84 and the node degree median is 2.

The nodes with highest degree centrality are: 866670 (degree 2624), 1294658 (degree 898), 8246 (degree 878), 328094 (degree 867) and 8992 (degree 860).
